<h3 id="get-service-bindings">GET Service Bindings</h3>

<p>Get all service bindings for a service instance</p>
<pre class="highlight shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://example.com/api/instances/{efb3c8ed-c176-4069-ae06-970b762f925f}/bindings"</span> <span class="se">\ </span>
    -X GET <span class="se">\ </span>
    -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: Bearer UAA_ACCESS_TOKEN"</span>
</code></pre>
